lyrics:
Yeah, yeah
Ayo, Elias, it's time.
It's time, Elias (aight, Elias, begin).
Straight out the smooth dungeons of rap.

The rod drops deep as does my love.
I never roam, 'cause to roam is the neve of dove.
Beyond the walls of thoughts, life is defined.
I think of rappers when I'm in an Amberg state of mind.

Hope the dove got some belove.
My truelove don't like no dirty shove.
Run up to the foxglove and get the glove.
In an Amberg state of mind. 
I can buy myself flowers
Write my name in the sand
Talk to myself for hours
Say things you don't understand
I can take myself dancing
And I can hold my own hand
Yeah, I can love me better than you can

Can love me better, I can love me better, baby
Can love me better, I can love me better, baby
